DarkMouse:: 

She saw how KitKat had created the clones. Now she was going to bring 
back her leader. Hopefully, she would restore the order in the group.

She reached into the bin and raised up KitKat's arm.  She pulled out 
her dagger and cut off the index finder of her left hand.  She then 
put the arm down and closed the bin.  She put the finger in the 
machine and turned it on.  The machine started to analize the DNA and 
started to regenerate the bot.  The computer would take a long time 
to take the venom from the DNA, but it would eventually create a new 
KitKat.  She smiled and went back to the bridge.

She sat back down in her chair and monitored the bots in the base.
